OL,3,CScottish and Irish rocks may be rare
OL,4,Crecord of 'snowball Earth', study
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,F"All complex, multicellular life, such
OL,8,Fas animals, arose out of this deep
OL,9,Ffreeze, with the first evidence in the
OL,10,Ffossil record appearing shortly after
OL,11,Fthe planet thawed."
OL,13,FFirst author Elias Rugen, a PhD
OL,14,Fcandidate at UCL Earth Sciences, said:
OL,15,F"Our study provides the first
OL,16,Fconclusive age constraints for these
OL,17,FScottish and Irish rocks, confirming
OL,18,Ftheir global significance."
