OL,3,CScottish and Irish rocks may be rare
OL,4,Crecord of 'snowball Earth', study
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,F"As soon as the world warmed up, all
OL,8,Fof life would have had to compete in
OL,9,Fan arms race to adapt. Whatever
OL,10,Fsurvived were the ancestors of all
OL,11,Fanimals."
OL,13,FFor the new study, the research team
OL,14,Fanalysed samples of sandstone from
OL,15,FPort Askaig Formation as well as from
OL,16,Fthe older, 70-metre thick Garbh
OL,17,FEileach Formation underneath.
